### Added missed plugin field for the Prettier config example

### Whit the old example, the file's list context menu actions missing the Format Code for the Apex.
### Old `.prettierrc` file example
```
{
  "trailingComma": "none",
  "overrides": [
    {
      "files": "**/lwc/**/*.html",
      "options": { "parser": "lwc" }
    },
    {
      "files": "*.{cmp,page,component}",
      "options": { "parser": "html" }
    }
  ]
}
```

### New `.prettierrc` file example
```
{
    "plugins": ["prettier-plugin-apex"],
    "trailingComma": "none",
    "overrides": [
        {
            "files": "**/lwc/**/*.html",
            "options": { "parser": "lwc" }
        },
        {
            "files": "*.{cmp,page,component}",
            "options": { "parser": "html" }
        }
    ]
}
```
